description: This big ole truck is serving up the tastiest comfort cravings in all the Twin Cities. The burgers are juicy, the tacos hit the spot, the gyros are perfect, the cheesesteaks are authentically delicious, and the Italian ice is so sweetly refreshing. For all this and more, come on by or have them cater your next occasion, because this wife may be crazy, but her food sure is insanely amazing.
name: My Crazy Wife's Italian Ice
